node.text:
GIVEAWAY TIME! We teamed up with the legends at @catchsurf and are giving away one 8’ soft top shred sled and a year supply of @kookslamshardseltzer 

To enter follow @catchsurf and @kookslamshardseltzer and tag two kooks in the comments section. Giveaway ends 9/24. Must be 21+ to enter 🤙
